<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<workout_file>
  <author>Gravel God Training</author>
  <name>W01_Tue_May4_FTP_Test</name>
  <description>[MODERATE FUEL: Target 30-60g carbs/hr. Stay topped up.]

Save - Week 1/6 - 6 weeks to Wish One Millau
Phase: BASE

WARM-UP:
-20min building from Z1 to Z2

MAIN SET:
-20min warmup with 3x1min blowouts, then 20min all-out. FTP = 95% of 20min power.
-Cadence: 90-95rpm - sustainable turnover
-Position: TT position if comfortable, otherwise drops

COOL-DOWN:
-10min easy spin Z1-Z2

PROGRESSION:
-Level 1/6: Introductory - Focus on form and learning the workout pattern
-Classic 20-minute test - pace conservatively first 5 minutes

PURPOSE:
Fitness assessment. Establish baseline metrics for training zones.

EXECUTION:
-Focus on consistent effort and good form throughout.

NUTRITION:
-40-60g carbs/hr for efforts over 60min.

HYDRATION:
-500-750ml/hr. Adjust for heat and humidity.</description>
  <sportType>bike</sportType>
  <workout>
    <Warmup Duration="1050" PowerLow="0.50" PowerHigh="0.75" />
    <SteadyState Duration="52" Power="1.20" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="105" Power="0.55" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="52" Power="1.20" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="105" Power="0.55" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="52" Power="1.20" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="105" Power="0.55" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <SteadyState Duration="262" Power="0.55" CadenceLow="90" CadenceHigh="95" />
    <FreeRide Duration="1200" FlatRoad="1" />
    <Cooldown Duration="525" PowerLow="0.75" PowerHigh="0.50" />
  </workout>
